snippet.title: Comet 64 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Comet 64 is a programming puzzle game. The year is 1984. All you got is a Comet 64 home computer and the operator's manual it came with.

Buy on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1397290/Comet_64/

Join the mailing list:
https://whatsorceressthis.com

Follow me on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/onurayas
